Name: assign_worker_to_team
Description: Binary decision to assign a worker to a team

Name: select_feature_for_sprint
Description: Binary decision to include a feature in a sprint

Name: assign_task_to_worker
Description: Binary decision to assign a task to a specific worker

Name: worker_sprint_availability
Description: Continuous variable for a worker's available hours in a sprint

Name: story_point_estimate
Description: Integer variable for estimating a user story's complexity

Name: sprint_duration
Description: Integer variable for the length of a sprint in weeks

Name: team_size
Description: Integer variable for the number of workers on a team

Name: priority_level
Description: Integer variable for setting the priority of a feature (higher=more important)

Name: skill_proficiency_level
Description: Integer level representing a worker's proficiency in a skill

Name: blocker_resolution_capacity
Description: Continuous variable for team capacity dedicated to resolving blockers
